Package: nctools
Version: 0.2
Title: Tools for Manipulating netCDF Files
Description: Provides helper functions for creating, editing, subsetting,
    concatenating, and transforming netCDF files. The package includes
    utilities for writing arrays to netCDF, renaming variables and
    dimensions, changing longitude conventions, and applying summary
    functions over dimensions through 'ncdf4'.
